701230f-a.title: Bronx: Havemeyer Avenue - Blackrock Avenue
701230f-a.text:
Havemeyer Ave., at the N.E. corner of Blackrock Ave., showing three
units of the German Odd Fellows Home. The view is eastward from Watson
AVe.
July 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
